Each of the judges of the Court for Calvert County shall receive as annual compensation the sum of:
$8,000 for calendar year 2006;
$8,250 for calendar year 2007;
$8,500 for calendar year 2008; and
$8,750 for calendar year 2009 and each subsequent calendar year.

The salary of the Chief Judge is:
$8,200 for calendar year 2006;
$8,450 for calendar year 2007;
$8,700 for calendar year 2008; and
$8,950 for calendar year 2009 and each subsequent calendar year.

Each of the judges of the Court for St. Mary's County shall receive an annual salary of:
$6,000 for the calendar year 2007;
$6,500 for the calendar year 2008;
$7,000 for the calendar year 2009; and
$7,500 for the calendar year 2010.
